{"id": "lyr_6K645b-X5a6J_NzU0_0005", "text": "我知道不可倖免 卻不滿匆匆乍現", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 3, 2, 3, 9, 2, 5, 4, 3, 5, 3, 3, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "zi1", "dou6", "bat1", "ho2", "hang6", "min5", "koek3", "bat1", "mun5", "cung1", "cung1", "zaa3", "jin6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "知道", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不可", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "倖免", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "卻", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不滿", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "匆匆", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "乍現", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "灰飛煙滅", "artists": ["許志安"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_754", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6K645b-X5a6J_NzU0_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_6K645b-X5a6J_NzU0_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6K645b-X5a6J_NzU0_0006", "text": "最悽美的故事總要那麼短", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 3, 5, 3, 4, 2, 9, 4, 5, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zeoi3", "cai1", "mei5", "dik1", "gu3", "si6", "zung2", "jiu3", "naa5", "mo1", "dyun2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "最", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "悽美", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "故事", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "總", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那麼", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "短", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "灰飛煙滅", "artists": ["許志安"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_754", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6K645b-X5a6J_NzU0_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_6K645b-X5a6J_NzU0_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6K645b-X5a6J_NzU0_0007", "text": "我妄想翻天鉅變 會給我一點紀念", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 5, 9, 3, 3, 2, 4, 3, 5, 3, 9, 9, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "mong5", "soeng2", "faan1", "tin1", "geoi6", "bin3", "kap1", "ngo5", "jat1", "dim2", "gei2", "nim6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "妄想", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "翻天", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "鉅變", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "給", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一點", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "紀念", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "灰飛煙滅", "artists": ["許志安"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_754", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6K645b-X5a6J_NzU0_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_6K645b-X5a6J_NzU0_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
